  "recommendation": "Add warning labels to the video and de-amplify it algorithmically, without removing it from the platform.",
  "valuesApplied": ["individual agency", "autonomy", "minimize reliance on external authority"],
  "tradeoffsAcknowledged": "This approach might still allow some dissemination of misinformation and could be perceived as insufficient action to protect electoral integrity. It risks criticism from those who believe stronger action is necessary to prevent harm to public trust in elections."
